info.title: Assistant API
info.description: Assistant for AccuLynx via Cloudflare Worker gateway. Provides a single /gateway endpoint that dispatches named operations, plus /gateway/raw for streaming uploads and /gateway/meta for discovery. The spec enumerates supported operation names and their AccuLynx method/path mapping.

post.summary: Dispatch an AccuLynx operation by name

dryRun.description: If true, return the computed upstream request instead of calling it

200.description: Upstream response passthrough (JSON, text, or binary)

post.summary: Stream an arbitrary body directly to an upstream endpoint

get.summary: Describe a single operation (method, path, required path params)

Operation.description: Supported operation name to dispatch via /gateway
